  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t我对他兴趣主要在影视, 但这个对习主席看来很有杀伤力<br/>\n<br/>\r\n转载一下<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9mb3J1bS5pYXNrLmNhL2NhbmFkYW1lZXQvdG9waWMvNjY0NTYz\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://forum.iask.ca/canadameet/topic/664563\">https://forum.iask.ca/canadameet/topic/664563</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<blockquote>薄案五天的庭审中，前四天主要是纠缠于案件的各种细节、证据，以及薄不知情的自辩，第五天（8月26日）的庭审中，薄熙来最后的总结陈述部分，官方公布了仅有1100字的版本，文气支离，逻辑也似乎有跳跃。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n此次“老董”公布薄熙来最终陈述版本则有2084字。今天（8月29日），本台从旁听薄熙来案5天庭审的知情者证实，这一版本除了个别语句表述外，基本属实。</blockquote><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9pbWd1ci5jb20vU0xrOG9ncw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://imgur.com/SLk8ogs\">https://imgur.com/SLk8ogs</a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9TTGs4b2dzLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/SLk8ogs.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/SLk8ogs.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SLk8ogs.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9rZFlXMldVLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/kdYW2WU.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kdYW2WU.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kdYW2WU.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9tQ1Yyc05lX2Qud2VicD9tYXh3aWR0aD03NjAmZmlkZWxpdHk9Z3JhbmQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/mCV2sNe_d.webp?maxwidth=760&amp;fidelity=grand\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mCV2sNe_d.webp?maxwidth=760&amp;fidelity=grand\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mCV2sNe_d.webp?maxwidth=760&amp;fidelity=grand\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
